seo: 泛微OA,SQL注入漏洞,E-Mobile4.0-6.6,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测泛微OA E-Mobile4.0-6.6版本中的SQL注入漏洞，通过发送特定请求并分析响应结果来确认是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect SQL injection vulnerabilities in Weaver OA E-Mobile version 4.0-6.6. It sends specific requests and analyzes the response to confirm whether the vulnerability exists.
